highlights.text: “Baila de Gasolina” by Effe Serieus has been on Viral Songs Netherlands the longest, at 209 days straight.
Beste Zangers has the most spots on Viral Songs Netherlands. “Kan Je Me Zien” is the highest at #5.
“Shiny” by Easykid and Dysbit is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Netherlands, up 1 spots at #8.
“Helaas” by Langa, Yssi SB, and Rijck is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Netherlands at #1.
